  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Long username overlaps done button. Instead, name should have dynamic font that gets smaller if there is no space.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nUsername does not overlap other texts.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7532782/40421288-acb859f4-5e8b-11e8-87f9-55ef9ac181d9.png\" width=\"200\">\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Set long username\r\n- Open contact code sharing screen and check the titlebar\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: nightly, May 23\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS",
